  <description><![CDATA[<p>On the edge of Zürs town centre i<span>n a quiet location</span>, the Hotel Edelweiss is an eclectic hotel with great access to the slopes. The family-run hotel has a traditional atmosphere that you would expect from an Austrian hotel with colourful interior design. </p>
<p>You will be based just 150 metres from the nearest lifts and you have access to the whole <a data-udi="umb://document/c24998bb7c5140ed8ec0febaf0a46fa2" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c24998bb7c5140ed8ec0febaf0a46fa2}" title="Arlberg Ski Area">Arlberg Ski Area</a>, the <span>largest interlinked ski area in Austria. The bus stops right outside the hotel and you are able to explore all <a data-udi="umb://document/754fd3eb2ae94fa89ed0dfc04d2b29b6" href="/{localLink:umb://document/754fd3eb2ae94fa89ed0dfc04d2b29b6}" title="Zurs">Zürs</a> has to offer in your central location.</span></p>
<p>Choose from a selection of rooms from the Double Superior up to the Superior Suite which can sleep up to five. All rooms are uniquely decorated with bold patterns and colourful designs. </p>
<p>The Hotel Edelweiss has a small wellness area with sauna, steam room and cold tub to enjoy after a day on the slopes. </p>
<h3>Exclusive to Inghams</h3>
<p>As a ski specialist tour operator we carefully select the very best accommodation in our resorts and package them with flights and transfers, so that you can make the most of your holiday. We have an exclusive agreement with Hotel Edelweiss the only UK tour operator to package and sell holidays here - all the more reason to book with Inghams today!</p>]]></description>
