  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Double Superior</strong> rooms are Austrian twins around 30m² and have a seating area and bath or shower. These rooms can sleep up to three.</p>
<p><strong>Double Deluxe</strong> rooms are slightly larger at 35m² and can sleep up to four.</p>
<p><strong>Junior Suite</strong> is 45m² and has a seating area, bath, and shower. They can sleep four using a double sofa bed.</p>
<p><strong>Tower Rooms</strong> are even more spacious at 60m² with lots of windows to let in light. They have a bath or shower and can sleep up to four.</p>
<p><strong>Superior Suite</strong> is the largest room at 70m² with separate living area, bath, and shower. They can sleep up to five.</p>]]></roomsDescription>
